latestPosts.caption:
Yoga for me has been about realising my better self. 

It feels like a dance sometimes, where @rutviq’s guidance is the music, uniting our mind, soul and breath. Holding a beautiful form that will take it shapes with this journey of conscious practise. 

This shoot was a fun way to bid goodbye to our time with @rutviq. 
Captured by the stunning @tanya.agarwall_ . Groomed by the sweetest @cletusliuu. Performed by new friends @gauteam @priyankabose20 

Styled in garments and accessories from our collective wardrobes.
